704622f-a.title: Brooklyn: Gerritsen Avenue - Plumb 1st Street
704622f-a.text:
(1)
Gerritsen Creek, fron Plumb 1st Street, on the east, and Ebony
Coort, on the west, and southward to the Atlantic Ocean. This
inlet will be filled in far the Marine Park development.
September 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, another view south.
September 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)
The same, a view southward.
September 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(4)
The same, another view.
September 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
